goal.tools.mc.core

Class Jenkins

  • java.lang.Object
    • goal.tools.mc.core.Jenkins

  • public class Jenkins
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents Jenkins' hash function lookup3. The function was originally written in C by Jenkins. This Java implementation is based on the C code, which can be found at http://www.burtleburtle.net/bob/c/lookup3.c.
    Author:
    sungshik

    • Method Detail

      • apply

        public static int[] apply(byte[] key,
          int pc,
          int pb)
        Apply Jenkins' hash function. It assumes a big endian representation, which is justified since the JVM uses big endian. The implementation is based on Jenkins' C code.
        Parameters:
        key - - The key to compute the hash code(s) for.
        length - - The length of the key.
        pc - - The seed for the first hash code.
        pb - - The seed for the second hash code.
        Returns:
        Two hash codes for key
